# SBO Wiki Scripts Rules

## Extraction

- Uses MediaWiki API (no auth required)
- 1.5 s delay between API batches; retries with backoff on 429/5xx
- Run: `node scripts/wiki-extract.js`

## Output

Writes to `data/wiki-raw/`:
- `weapons.json`, `armor.json`, `shields.json`, `bosses.json`, `stats-page.json`

## Parsers

Import from `parse-templates.js`:
- `parseWeaponTemplate`, `parseArmorTemplate`, `parseMobsTemplate`
- `parseTemplate`, `parseWikitable` for generic use

## Logging

Errors and progress log to `scripts/wiki-extract.log`.
